Type: Package
Package: concom
Title: Connected Components of an Undirected Graph
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Stéphane", "Laurent", , "laurent_step@outlook.fr",
        role = c("cre", "aut"))
Maintainer: Stéphane Laurent <laurent_step@outlook.fr>
Description: Provides a function for fast computation of the connected
        components of an undirected graph (though not faster than the
        components() function of the 'igraph' package) from the edges
        or the adjacency matrix of the graph. Based on this one, a
        function to compute the connected components of a triangle
        'rgl' mesh is also provided.
